00:00:06.474 --> 00:01:03.810 align:middle line:90%


00:01:03.810 --> 00:01:08.220 align:middle line:84%
>> In 1970, 44 years ago
when I was a young man,

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:09.660 align:middle line:90%
I had a near-death experience.

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:13.470 align:middle line:10%
I was killed in a motorcycle
wreck in Eugene, Oregon.

00:01:13.470 --> 00:01:18.520 align:middle line:84%
And I happened to have this
wreck in front of an ambulance

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.320 align:middle line:90%
location.

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:20.987 align:middle line:84%
And they just came
around, picked me up,

00:01:20.987 --> 00:01:22.330 align:middle line:90%
and took me to the hospital.

00:01:22.330 --> 00:01:25.770 align:middle line:84%
They put me in the ICU,
the intensive care unit.

00:01:25.770 --> 00:01:29.030 align:middle line:84%
And about three hours
later, I went into a coma.

00:01:29.030 --> 00:01:31.500 align:middle line:84%
I had rather extensive--
there's scars here

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:33.480 align:middle line:90%
on my wrist and stuff.

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:34.710 align:middle line:90%
Leg injuries.

00:01:34.710 --> 00:01:36.660 align:middle line:90%
I have steel in my femur here.

00:01:36.660 --> 00:01:42.750 align:middle line:84%
I have lost the kneecap
on my right leg.

00:01:42.750 --> 00:01:45.360 align:middle line:84%
Part of my wrist was
up here by my elbow,

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:47.160 align:middle line:90%
pushed up under the skin.

00:01:47.160 --> 00:01:50.460 align:middle line:90%
I was pretty well destroyed.

00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:52.640 align:middle line:84%
So three hours later,
I went into a coma,

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:55.820 align:middle line:90%
and I went out of body.

00:01:55.820 --> 00:01:57.960 align:middle line:84%
>> When I was about
five years old,

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:00.800 align:middle line:84%
I was recommended to go
in for a tonsillectomy

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:03.352 align:middle line:84%
because my tonsils were
supposedly infected.

00:02:03.352 --> 00:02:05.810 align:middle line:84%
And it turned out that they
actually weren't, so the doctor

00:02:05.810 --> 00:02:06.740 align:middle line:90%
didn't take them out.

00:02:06.740 --> 00:02:10.009 align:middle line:84%
But I did go through
the operation.

00:02:10.009 --> 00:02:12.650 align:middle line:84%
What happened was they took
me into the operating room.

00:02:12.650 --> 00:02:14.920 align:middle line:84%
And in those days,
they had a big mask

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.670 align:middle line:84%
that they put over you
for the anesthetic.

00:02:16.670 --> 00:02:18.830 align:middle line:84%
It was a little
different than nowadays.

00:02:18.830 --> 00:02:21.800 align:middle line:84%
And when they put the
mask over my face,

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:24.590 align:middle line:84%
he said, you know, he just said,
breathe deeply, so I breathed,

00:02:24.590 --> 00:02:27.410 align:middle line:84%
and it was OK pretty much,
except that of course,

00:02:27.410 --> 00:02:30.320 align:middle line:84%
I went out right away, which
I would, being five, you know?

00:02:30.320 --> 00:02:31.248 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

00:02:31.248 --> 00:02:32.640 align:middle line:90%


00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:36.070 align:middle line:84%
The next thing I knew, I
just shot up out of my body.

00:02:36.070 --> 00:02:39.600 align:middle line:84%
And for a while, I looked
down and saw myself

00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:41.070 align:middle line:90%
being operated on and stuff.

00:02:41.070 --> 00:02:43.320 align:middle line:84%
And I said, hmm, that's
interesting, you know?

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:46.020 align:middle line:84%
I was just looking
at myself and them.

00:02:46.020 --> 00:02:46.902 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

00:02:46.902 --> 00:02:49.550 align:middle line:90%


00:02:49.550 --> 00:02:53.450 align:middle line:84%
>> I became aware of my
clairvoyance at the age of 14

00:02:53.450 --> 00:02:55.310 align:middle line:90%
through a near-death experience.

00:02:55.310 --> 00:03:00.410 align:middle line:84%
Off and on for six years,
I just came to a point

00:03:00.410 --> 00:03:05.600 align:middle line:84%
where I began to
hear, feel, and see.

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:09.400 align:middle line:10%
I had a second near-death
experience at 41

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:13.110 align:middle line:10%
in a head-on collision.

00:03:13.110 --> 00:03:15.470 align:middle line:84%
And that experience,
all I can remember

00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:20.550 align:middle line:84%
is rising above my body
into a vibrant green light.

00:03:20.550 --> 00:03:26.180 align:middle line:84%
And when the two cars hit,
I never felt anything.

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:27.890 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't present.

00:03:27.890 --> 00:03:31.500 align:middle line:84%
It was as if I was
hovering above my body.

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:34.910 align:middle line:90%
I could see myself very clearly.

00:03:34.910 --> 00:03:37.760 align:middle line:84%
I could see myself
three dimensionally.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:41.180 align:middle line:84%
My consciousness was
floating above my body.

00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:43.490 align:middle line:84%
The thinking part
of me was up here.

00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:47.540 align:middle line:84%
This down here just felt like
a shell, but it was my shell.

00:03:47.540 --> 00:03:50.670 align:middle line:90%


00:03:50.670 --> 00:03:58.380 align:middle line:10%
>> I totaled my automobile and
my spirit and soul immediately

00:03:58.380 --> 00:04:02.970 align:middle line:10%
left my body in the car and
went through the tunnel we hear

00:04:02.970 --> 00:04:07.710 align:middle line:10%
people talk about quickly, all
the way through to the other

00:04:07.710 --> 00:04:12.030 align:middle line:10%
end and out the other end
into pure white light.

00:04:12.030 --> 00:04:15.870 align:middle line:84%
I also was spoken to with a
voice, what some people call

00:04:15.870 --> 00:04:17.355 align:middle line:90%
a conversation with God.

00:04:17.355 --> 00:04:20.339 align:middle line:90%


00:04:20.339 --> 00:04:24.450 align:middle line:84%
I was told immediately when
I entered the pure light

00:04:24.450 --> 00:04:27.030 align:middle line:90%
by a male voice--

00:04:27.030 --> 00:04:28.860 align:middle line:84%
and we all hear
whatever voice we

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:30.870 align:middle line:84%
need to hear in whatever
language in which

00:04:30.870 --> 00:04:32.280 align:middle line:90%
we need to hear it--

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:34.950 align:middle line:84%
telling me, Lewis,
you were called here

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:38.360 align:middle line:84%
to have this conversation and
to be sent back, because you

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:39.690 align:middle line:90%
are not doing your work.

00:04:39.690 --> 00:04:43.040 align:middle line:90%


00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:46.790 align:middle line:84%
>> The being of light
is definitely a being,

00:04:46.790 --> 00:04:50.660 align:middle line:84%
but not with a face, a
figure, anything else.

00:04:50.660 --> 00:04:53.300 align:middle line:90%
It's more of an energy center.

00:04:53.300 --> 00:04:56.330 align:middle line:84%
It's a white light that's
described as having gold

00:04:56.330 --> 00:04:58.200 align:middle line:90%
around the edges, if you wish.

00:04:58.200 --> 00:05:01.040 align:middle line:84%
It's the brightest,
prettiest, most loving light

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.090 align:middle line:90%
I've ever seen.

00:05:02.090 --> 00:05:07.100 align:middle line:84%
I've never been so in love
or at home or with my family

00:05:07.100 --> 00:05:08.310 align:middle line:90%
or with--

00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:10.340 align:middle line:90%
it's where I'm from.

00:05:10.340 --> 00:05:15.770 align:middle line:10%
And I felt that this being and
I had known each other for--

00:05:15.770 --> 00:05:18.590 align:middle line:10%
I used the term thousands
of years or eons.

00:05:18.590 --> 00:05:19.870 align:middle line:90%
We'd always known each other.

00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:21.920 align:middle line:84%
There was no beginning,
no end to how long

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:23.880 align:middle line:90%
we've known each other.

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:26.420 align:middle line:84%
If you think of each of
our consciousnesses as one

00:05:26.420 --> 00:05:29.270 align:middle line:84%
little grain of sand and
infinite intelligence

00:05:29.270 --> 00:05:32.720 align:middle line:84%
as the whole beach of sand,
I was plugged back in.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:35.780 align:middle line:84%
My little grain of sand was back
on the beach where I belonged,

00:05:35.780 --> 00:05:36.590 align:middle line:90%
where I came from.

00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:39.680 align:middle line:90%


00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:44.480 align:middle line:84%
>> And then I saw somebody
come up to me in a black dress,

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:48.240 align:middle line:84%
and it was my great grandmother
whom I'd actually known until I

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:49.040 align:middle line:90%
was about--

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:51.320 align:middle line:84%
well, she died when I was,
I think, two and a half,

00:05:51.320 --> 00:05:52.550 align:middle line:90%
or something like that.

00:05:52.550 --> 00:05:53.537 align:middle line:90%
I called her Gaga.

00:05:53.537 --> 00:05:54.620 align:middle line:90%
Everybody called her that.

00:05:54.620 --> 00:05:57.680 align:middle line:84%
And I said, oh, Gaga, I haven't
seen you in such a long time.

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:58.610 align:middle line:90%
And I put out my hand.

00:05:58.610 --> 00:06:02.720 align:middle line:84%
She took my hand and she
said, well, you're just here

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:06.230 align:middle line:90%
for a little visit.

00:06:06.230 --> 00:06:10.730 align:middle line:84%
I remember being in a corridor,
like a building that we

00:06:10.730 --> 00:06:11.570 align:middle line:90%
had gone into.

00:06:11.570 --> 00:06:14.660 align:middle line:84%
And there was a long
corridor with doors off of it

00:06:14.660 --> 00:06:18.680 align:middle line:84%
like a school like
classrooms, different rooms.

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:21.530 align:middle line:84%
Well, they opened the door to
the classroom and they said,

00:06:21.530 --> 00:06:22.650 align:middle line:90%
you can look at this.

00:06:22.650 --> 00:06:23.900 align:middle line:90%
You know, this is a classroom.

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:25.790 align:middle line:90%
People are learning things.

00:06:25.790 --> 00:06:27.680 align:middle line:90%
And they were at a keyboard.

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:32.300 align:middle line:84%
They were actually-- and you
have to realize, this is 1951,

00:06:32.300 --> 00:06:34.500 align:middle line:90%
because I was born in 1945.

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:36.710 align:middle line:84%
There were no such things
as computers, especially

00:06:36.710 --> 00:06:37.640 align:middle line:90%
personal computers.

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:41.030 align:middle line:84%
They were big, huge, room-sized
things then, those days.

00:06:41.030 --> 00:06:44.585 align:middle line:84%
And nobody had ever heard
of such a thing, you know?

00:06:44.585 --> 00:06:46.340 align:middle line:84%
There were
typewriters, of course,

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:47.990 align:middle line:84%
but these were not
keyboards like that.

00:06:47.990 --> 00:06:51.350 align:middle line:84%
They had little squares
and they also lit up.

00:06:51.350 --> 00:06:54.950 align:middle line:84%
I could see the light underneath
them, like some of were blue

00:06:54.950 --> 00:06:57.020 align:middle line:84%
and some were red
and some were green.

00:06:57.020 --> 00:07:00.440 align:middle line:84%
And I remember that the
man told me, he said,

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:02.330 align:middle line:84%
you will see these
later in your life.

00:07:02.330 --> 00:07:05.430 align:middle line:90%


00:07:05.430 --> 00:07:08.740 align:middle line:84%
>> But you know, I did have
an encounter in that encounter

00:07:08.740 --> 00:07:13.660 align:middle line:84%
with a fellow who came to me
and introduced himself as Ben.

00:07:13.660 --> 00:07:17.860 align:middle line:84%
He said that he had come to
be with me in this moment

00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:21.040 align:middle line:84%
so that I would not have to
have the experience alone.

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:23.980 align:middle line:84%
And told me that the
only thing that I needed

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:26.260 align:middle line:84%
to know moving forward
from this experience

00:07:26.260 --> 00:07:28.780 align:middle line:84%
is that I did not have
anything to worry about,

00:07:28.780 --> 00:07:30.760 align:middle line:90%
because I was hurt.

00:07:30.760 --> 00:07:34.450 align:middle line:84%
I was hurt and I was trapped
in the car for 45 minutes.

00:07:34.450 --> 00:07:37.630 align:middle line:84%
But he had the most
beautiful eyes I've ever seen

00:07:37.630 --> 00:07:39.610 align:middle line:90%
and was very gentle.

00:07:39.610 --> 00:07:42.970 align:middle line:84%
He called me by name
from the first meeting.

00:07:42.970 --> 00:07:44.950 align:middle line:84%
He spoke very softly
and very gently.

00:07:44.950 --> 00:07:48.700 align:middle line:10%
As soon as he touched me,
I completely went limp.

00:07:48.700 --> 00:07:51.130 align:middle line:84%
But then as he stepped
back from the car,

00:07:51.130 --> 00:07:54.040 align:middle line:84%
he said, I have to
go now, and smiled

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:55.800 align:middle line:90%
and vanished in thin air.

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:58.450 align:middle line:84%
And I knew I had literally
been touched by an angel.

00:07:58.450 --> 00:08:02.990 align:middle line:90%


00:08:02.990 --> 00:08:07.620 align:middle line:84%
>> I was in this state
of consciousness,

00:08:07.620 --> 00:08:13.700 align:middle line:84%
which was with my soul and
my spirit at this source.

00:08:13.700 --> 00:08:16.820 align:middle line:84%
I was no longer
in my body at all.

00:08:16.820 --> 00:08:19.650 align:middle line:90%
I said, well, I surrender.

00:08:19.650 --> 00:08:20.450 align:middle line:90%
Take me.

00:08:20.450 --> 00:08:21.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm yours.

00:08:21.380 --> 00:08:23.720 align:middle line:90%
I will do your work.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:25.940 align:middle line:90%
And I was told immediately, no.

00:08:25.940 --> 00:08:27.890 align:middle line:84%
It's not my work you
need to do, Lewis.

00:08:27.890 --> 00:08:30.480 align:middle line:90%
It's your work.

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:34.370 align:middle line:84%
I then asked, well,
what is my work?

00:08:34.370 --> 00:08:37.909 align:middle line:84%
Since I was in a place
where all knowledge is known

00:08:37.909 --> 00:08:40.580 align:middle line:84%
and I could feel that,
I assumed I was going

00:08:40.580 --> 00:08:43.669 align:middle line:90%
to be told what my work is.

00:08:43.669 --> 00:08:47.870 align:middle line:10%
And instead of being
told, I was asked, well,

00:08:47.870 --> 00:08:51.560 align:middle line:10%
what is it that keeps you
from being all you are capable

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:53.570 align:middle line:10%
of being?

00:08:53.570 --> 00:08:57.470 align:middle line:84%
Well, I didn't know, because
I thought everything was fine.

00:08:57.470 --> 00:09:01.220 align:middle line:84%
So I felt something
about difference

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:03.530 align:middle line:84%
that prevented my
soul from connecting

00:09:03.530 --> 00:09:05.750 align:middle line:90%
with the soul of another.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:08.060 align:middle line:84%
I did not know how
to bridge the gap.

00:09:08.060 --> 00:09:10.640 align:middle line:84%
And when I said
this in the light,

00:09:10.640 --> 00:09:14.150 align:middle line:84%
in my conversation
with God, then just

00:09:14.150 --> 00:09:16.580 align:middle line:84%
like the best moment
in the movie "Amadeus"

00:09:16.580 --> 00:09:18.530 align:middle line:84%
when Mozart hit a
perfect note and went,

00:09:18.530 --> 00:09:23.240 align:middle line:84%
there it is, the voice of God
said to me, there it is, Lewis.

00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:25.280 align:middle line:90%
There is your work.

00:09:25.280 --> 00:09:27.230 align:middle line:90%
And that was my conversation.

00:09:27.230 --> 00:09:30.690 align:middle line:84%
I was then sent back down
the entire same tunnel

00:09:30.690 --> 00:09:34.430 align:middle line:84%
in white light until I
remember coming into the body,

00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:37.460 align:middle line:90%
until those tight rubber gloves.

00:09:37.460 --> 00:09:39.060 align:middle line:90%
I'm not fully in until I am.

00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:39.860 align:middle line:90%
And then--

00:09:39.860 --> 00:09:40.240 align:middle line:90%
[POP]

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.040 align:middle line:90%
[WHOOSH]

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:42.890 align:middle line:84%
--this white light
disappeared, and I

00:09:42.890 --> 00:09:46.610 align:middle line:84%
was sitting in my automobile,
a totaled automobile, badly

00:09:46.610 --> 00:09:49.850 align:middle line:84%
damaged, with no
physical damage.

00:09:49.850 --> 00:09:52.635 align:middle line:84%
And I walked out of the car
into the ambulance to tell them,

00:09:52.635 --> 00:09:53.435 align:middle line:90%
there's no problem.

00:09:53.435 --> 00:09:56.800 align:middle line:90%


00:09:56.800 --> 00:09:59.430 align:middle line:84%
>> I was a young
man in my early 20s,

00:09:59.430 --> 00:10:02.030 align:middle line:90%
and I decided to come back here.

00:10:02.030 --> 00:10:04.830 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't done with the
reason I had been here.

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:09.390 align:middle line:84%
I clearly remember squeezing
down, getting smaller,

00:10:09.390 --> 00:10:11.310 align:middle line:90%
and coming into my body.

00:10:11.310 --> 00:10:16.900 align:middle line:84%
It was like slamming back into
the pain of this existence.

00:10:16.900 --> 00:10:20.460 align:middle line:84%
So I come back, and at that
time, a college student

00:10:20.460 --> 00:10:22.740 align:middle line:84%
studying mechanical
engineering and physics.

00:10:22.740 --> 00:10:27.230 align:middle line:84%
I come back into this life
and I go on with that career.

00:10:27.230 --> 00:10:28.980 align:middle line:84%
But they're teaching
me Newtonian physics.

00:10:28.980 --> 00:10:31.800 align:middle line:10%
They're teaching
me that 3D is it.

00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:34.530 align:middle line:10%
And I'm always, from the
beginning from then on,

00:10:34.530 --> 00:10:35.550 align:middle line:10%
I'm on the other side.

00:10:35.550 --> 00:10:36.560 align:middle line:90%
No, no.

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:38.167 align:middle line:84%
There's all the
rest of this energy.

00:10:38.167 --> 00:10:39.750 align:middle line:84%
There's all the rest
of this out here.

00:10:39.750 --> 00:10:44.000 align:middle line:90%


00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.750 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't remember going in
specifically to my body except

00:10:47.750 --> 00:10:52.880 align:middle line:84%
that, you know, it was like
going down a very small--

00:10:52.880 --> 00:10:54.880 align:middle line:84%
like a funnel or
something, you know?

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:57.380 align:middle line:84%
It was like I just
swooshed back in.

00:10:57.380 --> 00:10:59.000 align:middle line:84%
And I heard the
doctor say, I thought

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:01.130 align:middle line:84%
we were going to lose
her there for a minute.

00:11:01.130 --> 00:11:05.660 align:middle line:84%
I tried to lift my arm
and it felt so heavy

00:11:05.660 --> 00:11:07.190 align:middle line:90%
after having been really light.

00:11:07.190 --> 00:11:11.600 align:middle line:84%
And it was so nice being not
in a body, because everything

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:14.300 align:middle line:84%
was light and I could
just go where I wanted to

00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:15.740 align:middle line:90%
without even thinking.

00:11:15.740 --> 00:11:18.680 align:middle line:84%
And I tried to lift my
arm, and it weighed a ton.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:20.690 align:middle line:90%
And I thought to myself, oh, no.

00:11:20.690 --> 00:11:21.690 align:middle line:90%
Not this again.

00:11:21.690 --> 00:11:22.630 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

