00:12:14.910 --> 00:12:20.160 align:middle line:90%


00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:23.780 align:middle line:84%
>> First off, when I had the
near-death experience in 1970,

00:12:23.780 --> 00:12:25.490 align:middle line:90%
I started talking about it.

00:12:25.490 --> 00:12:27.230 align:middle line:84%
And I was on the
head injury floor,

00:12:27.230 --> 00:12:28.730 align:middle line:84%
and so the chief
psychiatrist wanted

00:12:28.730 --> 00:12:31.507 align:middle line:84%
