00:12:33.980 --> 00:12:35.600 align:middle line:90%
What is that, you know?

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:36.590 align:middle line:90%
You're crazy.

00:12:36.590 --> 00:12:38.270 align:middle line:84%
So he wants to throw
me in the nuthouse.

00:12:38.270 --> 00:12:40.060 align:middle line:90%
