00:12:40.060 --> 00:12:40.860 align:middle line:90%
They've heard.

00:12:40.860 --> 00:12:42.170 align:middle line:90%
They've seen it too many times.

00:12:42.170 --> 00:12:43.795 align:middle line:84%
And they're hugging
me and saying, shh.

00:12:43.795 --> 00:12:44.720 align:middle line:90%
Don't.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:45.610 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, but it's true.

00:12:45.610 --> 00:12:46.740 align:middle line:90%
I've got to tell him.

00:12:46.740 --> 00:12:48.950 align:middle line:84%
So he's saying to me, so
you think you're Jesus?

00:12:48.950 --> 00:12:49.770 align:middle line:90%
And I say, look.

00:12:49.770 --> 00:12:50.570 align:middle line:90%
I went there.

00:12:50.570 --> 00:12:51.370 align:middle line:90%
I did it.

00:12:51.370 --> 00:12:52.520 align:middle line:90%
