00:12:55.370 --> 00:12:57.080 align:middle line:84%
And you're telling
me it doesn't exist

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:58.830 align:middle line:90%
because you have a degree?

00:12:58.830 --> 00:13:01.160 align:middle line:84%
I believe they may have
given my body painkillers,

00:13:01.160 --> 00:13:02.910 align:middle line:90%
but I was out of the body.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:05.120 align:middle line:84%
So people say, well, it's
a drug effect in your mind.

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:06.620 align:middle line:90%
No, I'm out of the body.

00:13:06.620 --> 00:13:08.210 align:middle line:84%
I remember coming
back into the room

00:13:08.210 --> 00:13:10.340 align:middle line:84%
and coming back into the
body and seeing myself

00:13:10.340 --> 00:13:12.000 align:middle line:90%
and coming into it.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.670 align:middle line:84%
I finally get out
of the hospital.

00:13:13.670 --> 00:13:16.940 align:middle line:10%
I go to the pastor at
my church and he says,

00:13:16.940 --> 00:13:19.760 align:middle line:10%
well, it can't possibly
be true, because it

00:13:19.760 --> 00:13:21.440 align:middle line:10%
doesn't agree with scripture.

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:22.680 align:middle line:10%
And I said, wait a minute.

00:13:22.680 --> 00:13:24.620 align:middle line:10%
It doesn't agree with
your interpretation

00:13:24.620 --> 00:13:25.900 align:middle line:10%
of the scripture.

00:13:25.900 --> 00:13:26.700 align:middle line:90%
It's true.

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:27.500 align:middle line:90%
I went there.

00:13:27.500 --> 00:13:30.190 align:middle line:90%


00:13:30.190 --> 00:13:32.850 align:middle line:84%
Those people who want to
say, well, it was a drug,

00:13:32.850 --> 00:13:36.280 align:middle line:84%
or well, it was
something else, they're

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:38.530 align:middle line:84%
looking for it to be something
else because they don't

00:13:38.530 --> 00:13:40.690 align:middle line:90%
want to hear what we're saying.

00:13:40.690 --> 00:13:43.210 align:middle line:84%
>> I would say not to let
other people discourage you.

00:13:43.210 --> 00:13:44.837 align:middle line:84%
Some people let
other people say,

00:13:44.837 --> 00:13:46.420 align:middle line:84%
oh, well, you couldn't
have seen that,

00:13:46.420 --> 00:13:48.253 align:middle line:84%
or you couldn't have--
you know, da, da, da.

00:13:48.253 --> 00:13:51.550 align:middle line:84%
And of course, I would say,
believe in what you have seen

00:13:51.550 --> 00:13:52.900 align:middle line:90%
and what you've experienced.

00:13:52.900 --> 00:13:57.850 align:middle line:84%
If you did experience
this, it's a good thing.

00:13:57.850 --> 00:13:59.470 align:middle line:90%
>> There was no confusion.

00:13:59.470 --> 00:14:01.270 align:middle line:90%
This was not a dream.

00:14:01.270 --> 00:14:07.120 align:middle line:10%
This was my real experience
of my soul outside of my body,

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:10.330 align:middle line:10%
outside of my personality,
outside of my ego,

00:14:10.330 --> 00:14:13.060 align:middle line:10%
and outside of my
human form having

00:14:13.060 --> 00:14:19.570 align:middle line:10%
a real experience at what I
call the source of all energy,

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:24.430 align:middle line:10%
and all spirit from
which we all come.

00:14:24.430 --> 00:14:26.500 align:middle line:84%
Just when I say I've
been in the light

00:14:26.500 --> 00:14:29.530 align:middle line:84%
and experienced all
knowledge where there's

00:14:29.530 --> 00:14:34.820 align:middle line:84%
nothing but love and light
and truth and peace and grace,

00:14:34.820 --> 00:14:38.350 align:middle line:84%
there's still not enough when
you add all the words together

00:14:38.350 --> 00:14:41.080 align:middle line:84%
to fully describe
what I experienced.

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:43.390 align:middle line:84%
>> It was more real
than this reality.

00:14:43.390 --> 00:14:46.360 align:middle line:84%
We all remember that
experience better

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:48.160 align:middle line:90%
than anything else in our life.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:49.510 align:middle line:90%
It is embedded in us.

00:14:49.510 --> 00:14:52.900 align:middle line:84%
It is burned into our mind,
because it was more real.

00:14:52.900 --> 00:14:55.520 align:middle line:90%


00:14:55.520 --> 00:14:59.580 align:middle line:84%
So for people,
how to believe it?

00:14:59.580 --> 00:15:01.330 align:middle line:84%
They always want me
to give them that one.

00:15:01.330 --> 00:15:02.680 align:middle line:90%
How to believe it?

00:15:02.680 --> 00:15:04.000 align:middle line:90%
Walk a mile in my shoes?

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.650 align:middle line:84%
Go have your own
