00:17:21.140 --> 00:17:25.460 align:middle line:10%
scientifically, because our
understanding of the word

00:17:25.460 --> 00:17:29.780 align:middle line:10%
memory is that it
is in the brain.

00:17:29.780 --> 00:17:35.390 align:middle line:84%
And the brain was in the body,
and the body was in the car.

00:17:35.390 --> 00:17:39.800 align:middle line:84%
So no, I cannot prove to you
scientifically how I can have

00:17:39.800 --> 00:17:42.500 align:middle line:84%
perfect memory of
this experience.

00:17:42.500 --> 00:17:45.680 align:middle line:84%
>> In standard practice
in neurosurgery,

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:49.140 align:middle line:84%
the belief is that the brain
creates a consciousness.

00:17:49.140 --> 00:17:51.290 align:middle line:84%
This is a thing we're
taught in grade school,

00:17:51.290 --> 00:17:53.630 align:middle line:84%
that the brain makes
the consciousness.

00:17:53.630 --> 00:17:57.800 align:middle line:84%
The truth is-- and physics is
coming up against this one big

00:17:57.800 --> 00:17:58.700 align:middle line:90%
time now--

00:17:58.700 --> 00:18:01.640 align:middle line:84%
the truth is that the
consciousness makes the brain,

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:04.860 align:middle line:90%
and not the other way around.

00:18:04.860 --> 00:18:06.910 align:middle line:84%
The brain is just
like a television set.

00:18:06.910 --> 00:18:08.060 align:middle line:90%
It's a receiving station.

00:18:08.060 --> 00:18:11.130 align:middle line:84%
The consciousness
exists outside the body.

00:18:11.130 --> 00:18:13.700 align:middle line:84%
If you think about
your consciousness

00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:17.810 align:middle line:84%
as existing outside of your
body but telling itself

00:18:17.810 --> 00:18:20.615 align:middle line:84%
that the locus of your
consciousness is in your head,

00:18:20.615 --> 00:18:22.490 align:middle line:84%
so then you're going to
experience everything

00:18:22.490 --> 00:18:24.530 align:middle line:84%
inside of the body, then
you can see how easy

00:18:24.530 --> 00:18:26.240 align:middle line:90%
it is to go out of body.

00:18:26.240 --> 00:18:28.080 align:middle line:84%
You just shift where
you're thinking it is.

00:18:28.080 --> 00:18:28.880 align:middle line:90%
You say, OK.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:30.172 align:middle line:90%
I'm no longer in this computer.

00:18:30.172 --> 00:18:31.220 align:middle line:90%
I'm out here in this one.

00:18:31.220 --> 00:18:32.180 align:middle line:90%
Click.

00:18:32.180 --> 00:18:32.980 align:middle line:90%
Now I'm out there.

00:18:32.980 --> 00:18:33.780 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:18:33.780 --> 00:18:35.390 align:middle line:90%
Now I can look down on my body.

00:18:35.390 --> 00:18:38.240 align:middle line:84%
OK, if I want to make my locus
back inside the head, click.

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:39.650 align:middle line:90%
I'm back in here.

00:18:39.650 --> 00:18:43.240 align:middle line:84%
>> Can we demonstrate that
consciousness is non-local?

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:45.830 align:middle line:84%
And by that, meaning that
you can gain information

00:18:45.830 --> 00:18:48.350 align:middle line:84%
