00:18:51.380 --> 00:18:53.060 align:middle line:90%
whether that is possible.

00:18:53.060 --> 00:18:55.550 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that if
you dispassionately

00:18:55.550 --> 00:18:57.470 align:middle line:84%
look at the evidence
that is available,

00:18:57.470 --> 00:18:59.720 align:middle line:84%
then you will find
that the answer is yes,

00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:02.210 align:middle line:84%
or at least that we have high
confidence that the answer is

00:19:02.210 --> 00:19:04.340 align:middle line:84%
yes, and people can
gain information

00:19:04.340 --> 00:19:06.620 align:middle line:84%
from a distance
in space or time.

00:19:06.620 --> 00:19:09.320 align:middle line:84%
Maybe consciousness
requires the thing

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:13.340 align:middle line:84%
that we call the brain in order
to be aware, and maybe not.

00:19:13.340 --> 00:19:16.740 align:middle line:10%
Maybe any sufficiently
complex system would do,

00:19:16.740 --> 00:19:18.510 align:middle line:10%
but we don't know yet.

00:19:18.510 --> 00:19:21.820 align:middle line:84%
>> And since science does not
yet know how to explain all

00:19:21.820 --> 00:19:27.610 align:middle line:84%
this, there are many experiences
