00:19:46.420 --> 00:19:52.780 align:middle line:84%
That is where we now are in this
description of our experiences

00:19:52.780 --> 00:19:54.400 align:middle line:90%
out of our body.

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:57.890 align:middle line:84%
>> Unless we know what
consciousness is or awareness,

00:19:57.890 --> 00:20:00.010 align:middle line:90%
