aware of what I'm

00:20:05.590 --> 00:20:08.180 align:middle line:84%
capable of at an
unconscious level?

00:20:08.180 --> 00:20:10.100 align:middle line:84%
And the traditional
answer to that,

00:20:10.100 --> 00:20:12.340 align:middle line:84%
which I think is probably
the safest method,

00:20:12.340 --> 00:20:13.750 align:middle line:90%
is through meditation.

00:20:13.750 --> 00:20:17.200 align:middle line:84%
So meditation in many ways is
all about getting in contact

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:18.670 align:middle line:90%
with your unconscious.

00:20:18.670 --> 00:20:21.280 align:middle line:84%
You get to deeper and deeper
levels of awareness about

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:22.730 align:middle line:90%
what's going on.

00:20:22.730 --> 00:20:24.670 align:middle line:84%
And eventually, you reach
a level of awareness

00:20:24.670 --> 00:20:27.475 align:middle line:84%
where we might say that somebody
would become extremely psychic.

00:20:27.475 --> 00:20:31.270 align:middle line:90%


