couldn't have been too dead.

00:20:39.900 --> 00:20:43.860 align:middle line:84%
Just dead enough to be
declared near death.

00:20:43.860 --> 00:20:48.240 align:middle line:84%
And so we don't know what would
happen if a person actually

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:50.975 align:middle line:90%
dies and doesn't come back.

00:20:50.975 --> 00:20:52.350 align:middle line:84%
We don't know what
the answer is.

00:20:52.350 --> 00:20:56.120 align:middle line:90%


00:20:56.120 --> 00:20:57.980 align:middle line:84%
>> We all leave in
